{{Infobox dungeon |name = Po Town |image = [[File:Po Town.png|300px]] |caption = A map of Po Town. |tokens = 1,075,000 |location = North of Route 17 }}
'''Po Town''' is a [[Dungeons|dungeon]] in [[Alola]]. It initially has 121 tiles arranged in a 11x11 square, including 11 chest tiles, 41 non-boss encounter tiles, and 1 boss encounter tile. Wild Encounters have 15,340,576 HP.
